{"lemma":"مُجْتَمَع","slug":"مُجْتَمَع","root":"ج.م.ع","root_slug":"ج-م-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-م-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مُجْتَمَع","root":"جمع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6333","n6334"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%AC%D9%92%D8%AA%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"place of assembly"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"society","examples":[{"text":"يَلْعَبُ ٱلتَّعْلِيمُ دَوْرًا هَامًّا فِي تَنْمِيَةِ ٱلْمُجْتَمَعَاتِ.","english":"Education plays a crucial role in the development of societies."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"assembly"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"community"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Noun of place from the verb اِجْتَمَعَ (ijtamaʕa)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6333","headword_ar":"مُجْتَمَعٌ","root":"jmE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place in which a thing becomes collected, brought together, or the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which things have become so; where they collect themselves, come together,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unite;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which they are comprised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contained; a place in which is a collection of things"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbayoDapu","text_ar":"البَيْضَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mujotamaEu Alwaladi","text_ar":"مُجْتَمَعُ الوَلَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The egg is that which comprises the young bird"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"byD","text_ar":"بيض"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mujotamaEu","text_ar":"مُجْتَمَعُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almawoti","text_ar":"المَوْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawoDu Almawoti","text_ar":"حَوْضُ المَوْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which see, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HwD","text_ar":"حوض"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in that art.) ―         -b2-  [Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collective mass,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the hair of the head: (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~apN","text_ar":"جُمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mujotamaEu $aEori Alr~aA^osi","text_ar":"مُجْتَمَعُ شَعْرِ الرَّاْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the whole head of hair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majomaEN","text_ar":"مَجْمَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6334","headword_ar":"مُجْتَمِعٌ","root":"jmE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiyEN","text_ar":"جَمِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in five places. ―         -b2-  A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who has attained to his full state of manly vigour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and whose beard has become fullgrown:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) because at that time his powers have become collected, or because his beard is then full-grown. (Mgh.) [See the verb, 8. And see an ex. in a verse of Suheym Ibn-Wetheel cited in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dwr","text_ar":"دور"},{"kind":"text","text":", conj. 3.] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloqaAhu mujotamiEFA","text_ar":"اَلْقَاهُ مُجْتَمِعًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He threw him down gathered together,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a heap"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S and Msb and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kwr","text_ar":"كور"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aY mujotamiEFA","text_ar":"مَشَى مُجْتَمِعًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He walked quickly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with vehemence of motion, and strength of limbs, not languidly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","TA","K"]}]}}